---
title: Creamy Lemon & Prawn Orecchiette with Parsley & Chilli Flakes
description: A seafood pasta feels fancy without even trying and we think a squeeze of zesty lemon juice with these prawns is enough to
earn a five star rating for this orecchiette dish. We’ll let you be the judge.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-lemon-prawn-orecchiette-f35d893f.jpg
